text: Shh, sweetie. I know you need to sleep, but don't you?
Mmm, it's so annoying when you get those nights of insomnia.
Why don't I just tinkle you until you do fall asleep?
You always say to me that you tingle the most when you're on the cusp of sleep.
Shh, I love you very much.
Don't worry if I'm doing it for a while either.
I know how subconscious you can be.
Just let me show my love for you by doing this, okay?
